course_title: Intensive Specialized Chamber Ensemble - INT SPC CHMB ENS

sections.comments: MUSC 569 represents credit for the extra work that some students do in some ensembles and should involve 1 hr/week additional coaching time. Permission to take 569 must come from the division coordinator (via a signed drop/add form forwarded to the MUSC student advisor) who will coach you in either 560 or 562, because 569  has 560 or 562 as a co-requisite (as 569 represents "extra work" you are doing in 560 or 562).  Not for use by pianists.
